Oh, it's you!
I was actually worried for a minute.

1752
01:35:30,160 --> 01:35:31,832
- Keep your hands up.
- No!

1753
01:35:31,960 --> 01:35:34,235
- Put 'em up!
- I'll make a deal with you.

1754
01:35:34,360 --> 01:35:35,509
I'll put one up.

1755
01:35:35,640 --> 01:35:37,119
Put the other one up!

1756
01:35:37,960 --> 01:35:39,916
Which looks better?

1757
01:35:41,000 --> 01:35:43,309
I'm warning you, Otto.

1758
01:35:43,440 --> 01:35:44,873
What are you going to do?

1759
01:35:45,040 --> 01:35:48,112
