in cold blood, like a dog? Hey?

1760
01:35:48,240 --> 01:35:52,233
If you want to settle something,
fight me. You're a man.

1761
01:35:52,360 --> 01:35:54,316
Let's fight like men! Come on!

1762
01:35:55,520 --> 01:35:57,033
All right.

1763
01:35:57,160 --> 01:35:58,149
